headline: Block Inc (XYZ) Faces Mixed Outlook with Growth and Challenges
summary: Block Inc (NYSE:XYZ) is one of the best NYSE stocks to buy for the long term. On February 12, Morgan Stanley kept its Equalweight rating and $72 price target on Block Inc. (NYSE:XYZ), noting slower growth in Square’s payment volumes. The firm now expects Q4 2025 Seller GPV growth of 10.3% year‑over‑year, down from 12.7%, […]
